      </p>
      <p xml:space="preserve">
        <docTitle refersTo="#adoption">Adopted by the Security Council at its <inline name="adoptionMeeting" title="9169th">9169th meeting</inline>, on <docDate date="2022-10-27" refersTo="#adoptionDate">27 October 2022</docDate></docTitle>
